<html>
  <head>
    <title>Location-based Cooperative (LoCo) Login</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <table border="1" width=80%>
      <tr bgcolor="#4682B4">
         <th align="center" colspan=2><h2>Location-based Cooperative (LoCo) Login</h2></th>
      </tr>
      <tr bgcolor="#DBEAF5">
         <td valign="top" width=50%>
             <p>
             LoCo (Location-based Cooperative) allows people to cooperate on activities
             that are organized around locales. It allows users to add content-associated
             markers to a map and to view and search for markers based on selected criteria,
             such as content, dates, and user names and addresses.
         </td>
         <td align="center">
           <form method="post">
             <p>
             Please login
             <br><font color="red">%message%</font>
             <table>
               <tr>
               <td align="right"><label for="user">User name:</label></td><td><input type="text" name="user" id="user"></td>
               </tr>
               <tr>
               <td align="right"><label for="password">Password:</label></td><td><input type="password" name="password" id="password"></td>
               </tr>
               <tr>
               <p>
               <td>
               <input type="submit" name="login" value="Login">
               </td>
               <td>
               <input type="submit" name="register" value="Register">
               </td>
               </tr>
            </table>
           </form>
         </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </body>
</html>


